https://ycanfix.com/how-to-create-a-direct-download-button-in-elementor/

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bvV0mAcox5c

Step 1) Add the ID to the button:

<button id="btn-btn"> Download PDF </button>

Step 2) Add download | Name of the file without any space as mentioned on the screen:

Step 3) Add the Script code:

<script>
 
document.querySelector("#btn-btn").addEventListener("click", function(){
  document.querySelector("#btn-btn  .elementor-button-text").innerHTML = "Pdf is Downloading";
  document.querySelector("#btn-btn").style.display = "inline-block";
});
  
 </script>
